Ross Patterson, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, and Evan Hafer are joined by comedian and military veteran Jon Stites of Operation Comedy to chat about what it's like doing stand up comedy on USO Tours with Bill Burr, why Bachelorette parties are the worst, and how to spot someone who's probably writing a manifesto.
